ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc25ba065c0892ed32e1fa71ed60ba0ffca0fb1","tid":1867914,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c110c76deae1b5e4b471d4af3a8824dc99aee36e","tid":1867914,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於 失敗<br />\n如果一陣投票結果係唔繼續<br />\n都唔可以 spin 到係失敗<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d9f246baeec5aa02a424c8e3e60c35d56054ed0","tid":1867914,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"faec7d89318f506faff30389b82796bf362fb76a","tid":1867914,"uid":158504,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a8ae71d53f1cc5a184893d8c20eef93053be9770","tid":1867914,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"高登、香討、bk、yahoo、01等等，依家冇一個forum/留言區係同情理解醫護，全部都係落井下石緊，醫護所作嘅一切決定都要尊重，唔希望連登都係佢哋一份子！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"你以上講嘅forum已經比支那收編咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad